    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK935">
<l>kavaṟuṅ kaḻakamuṅ kaiyun tarukki</l>
<l>yivaṟiyā rillāki yār</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Penniless are those who by reason of their attachment would never forsake gambling, the gambling-place and the handling (of dice).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
